sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant Retrieval as Retrieval Service
    participant DB as IndexedDB
    participant AI as AI Provider
    participant Citation as Citation Mapper

    User->>UI: Ask question about documents
    UI->>Retrieval: Query + Document IDs
    Retrieval->>DB: Fetch chunks for documents
    DB-->>Retrieval: Relevant chunks
    Retrieval->>Retrieval: TF-IDF ranking, Top-K selection
    Retrieval-->>UI: Ranked chunks
    UI->>UI: Build prompt with context
    UI->>AI: Send prompt + context chunks
    AI-->>UI: AI response with citation IDs
    UI->>Citation: Resolve citation IDs
    Citation->>DB: Fetch chunk details
    DB-->>Citation: Full chunk data + document info
    Citation-->>UI: Resolved citations with source info
    UI-->>User: Display answer with clickable citations
    User->>UI: Click citation reference
    UI->>UI: Open Evidence Drawer
    UI-->>User: Show source document, page, excerpt, relation
